  <brief_title>Trial and Cost Effectiveness Evaluation of Intra-arterial Thrombectomy in Acute Ischemic Stroke</brief_title>
  <acronym>THRACE</acronym>
  <official_title>The Contribution of Intra-arterial Thrombectomy in Acute Ischemic Stroke in Patients Treated With Intravenous Thrombolysis</official_title>
